Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:55.94,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Why not 闘い得た　絆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:22:04.57,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Just now　この手の中で　熱く輝け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:17.25,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}One in a seven billion の憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:22.81,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Someday 世界が終わる日が　来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:28.01,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}So，What？　1ミリの悔いもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:33.73,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Say， yeah！！　一筋に走る流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:36.39,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}鼓動ドキドキ止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:41.14,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}迷いも全部　蹴っ飛ばせ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:46.66,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}宇宙に　抱かれし　蒼い地球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:51.93,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}いつも心に描く　エリシオン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:57.29,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}過去も未来も　自分が創る
